normalize seurat counts and store in object  
example:
restinglung.integrated2 <- getRC_object(object=restinglung.integrated2)

normalize expression of selected gene
addition arguments: mintotal=2000 scaling factor for normalization of counts, following RaceID mintotal argument
example
plotexpmap(restinglung.integrated2, "Tcf7", logsc = T, seurat = T, mintotal = 2000)
